# 🔍 Fodwa App — Full Architecture Audit Report

> **Date:** 2026-03-07 · **Scope:** Read-only analysis, no code modified

---

## 1. Project Summary

**Fodwa** is a Flutter mobile application (appears to be a professional services / logistics platform). It supports user authentication (email, phone, Google, Apple), profile management, trip/load management, a map-based location flow, help & support, and a chat feature (placeholder).

### Main User Flows
1. **Splash → Login / Sign Up** (email or phone, social auth)
2. **Forget Password → Verify Code → Reset**
3. **Email OTP Verification** after registration
4. **Home** (tabbed bottom nav with Home, Cars, Messages, Profile)
5. **Profile** — view / edit, upload images
6. **Help & Support** — FAQ / contact support

### Folder Structure

```
lib/
├── config/
│   ├── configeration/   ← (misspelled "configuration")
│   └── routes/
├── core/
│   ├── apiManager/
│   ├── cahsing/         ← (misspelled "caching")
│   ├── firebase/
│   ├── handleErrors/
│   ├── intialization/   ← (misspelled "initialization")
│   ├── networkError/
│   ├── session/
│   ├── sharedWidget/
│   └── utils/
├── features/
│   ├── Auth/            ← (login, signUp — Clean Architecture layers)
│   ├── bottom_nav/
│   ├── chat/
│   ├── helpAndSupport/
│   ├── home/
│   ├── profile/         ← (data/di/domain/presentation layers)
│   └── splash/
├── generated/           ← (easy_localization codegen)
└── main.dart
```

> [!WARNING]
> Three core directory names are misspelled: `cahsing`, `intialization`, `configeration`. This will cause confusion and refactoring pain later.

