## 2. Dependency Analysis

### pubspec.yaml — 40+ dependencies

| Package | Purpose | Issue |
|---------|---------|-------|
| `get: ^4.7.2` | GetX state management | **Never imported anywhere in lib/** — completely unused |
| `get_storage: ^2.1.1` | Key-value storage | Used for login flag only; redundant with `shared_preferences` |
| `shared_preferences: ^2.5.3` | Key-value storage | **Never imported** — unused |
| `flutter_secure_storage: ^9.2.4` | Encrypted storage | Used for auth token/userId |
| `flutter_bloc: ^9.1.1` + `bloc: ^9.1.0` | BLoC pattern | Primary state management |
| `get_it: ^9.0.5` | DI container | Used correctly |
| `firebase_core`, `firebase_auth`, `cloud_firestore` | Firebase | **`firebase_core` never initialized** in [main()](file:///f:/Fodwa-App-main/lib/main.dart#10-35). Firebase packages are declared but unused |
| `google_sign_in`, `sign_in_with_apple` | Social auth | API endpoints exist, but no Firebase initialization to back them |
| `google_maps_flutter`, `geolocator`, `geocoding` | Maps/Location | Used for location features |
| `device_preview: ^1.3.1` | Testing tool | **Should be dev_dependency**, currently in main dependencies |
| `shimmer_animation`, `skeletonizer`, `flutter_animate`, `animate_do`, `flutter_staggered_animations`, `motion`, `lottie` | Animations | **7 animation packages** — likely redundant overlap |
| `google_nav_bar`, `convex_bottom_bar`, `curved_navigation_bar` | Bottom nav | **3 bottom nav packages** — only a custom BottomAppBar is actually used |
| `cookie_jar`, `dio_cookie_manager` | Cookie persistence | Used with Dio |
| `path_provider` | _(implicit via dio)_ | Used in DioClient but **not declared** in pubspec.yaml |

> [!CAUTION]
> `path_provider` is used in [dio_client.dart](file:///f:/Fodwa-App-main/lib/core/apiManager/dio_client.dart) but **not listed as a dependency**. It works transitively but will break if transitive deps change.

### Packages to Remove (unused)
- [get](file:///f:/Fodwa-App-main/lib/core/session/session_manager.dart#43-46) (GetX) — never imported
- `shared_preferences` — never imported
- `google_nav_bar` — not used
- `convex_bottom_bar` — not used
- `curved_navigation_bar` — not used

### Packages to Move to dev_dependencies
- `device_preview`
- `flutter_launcher_icons`

