## 6. Performance Review

### Issues Detected

| Issue | Location | Severity |
|-------|----------|----------|
| **`tabs` list in [BottomNav](file:///f:/Fodwa-App-main/lib/features/bottom_nav/bottom_nav.dart#10-16)** | [bottom_nav.dart](file:///f:/Fodwa-App-main/lib/features/bottom_nav/bottom_nav.dart#L139-L145) — non-final field, recreated on every build | 🔴 High |
| **Missing `const` constructors** | `HomePageItem()`, [ProfileScreen()](file:///f:/Fodwa-App-main/lib/features/profile/presentation/pages/profile_screen.dart#7-13) in tabs list not `const` | ⚠️ Medium |
| **`print()` statements** | 8+ files contain `print()` calls for debugging — should use logger | ⚠️ Medium |
| **Verbose state emissions** | LoginBloc copies `isRemember`, `selectedTab`, `phoneNumber` on every emit — causes unnecessary object allocations | ⚠️ Medium |
| **BlocProvider in build()** | `LoginScreen._LoginScreenState.build()` creates `BlocProvider` inside build — recreated on every rebuild | 🔴 High |
| **`AppConstants.initSize` in build** | Called in both `SplashScreen.build()` and `BottomNav.build()` — doing `MediaQuery.of()` on every build | ⚠️ Low |
| **`addPostFrameCallback` in build** | [LoginScreen](file:///f:/Fodwa-App-main/lib/features/Auth/login/presentation/pages/login_screen.dart#22-31) adds post-frame callbacks in [build()](file:///f:/Fodwa-App-main/lib/features/Auth/signUp/presentation/pages/sign_up_screen.dart#22-80) which could fire multiple times | ⚠️ Medium |
| **`StatefulWidget` with no state** | [HomePage](file:///f:/Fodwa-App-main/lib/features/home/presentation/pages/home_page_item.dart#5-11) is StatefulWidget but holds no state — should be `StatelessWidget` | ⚠️ Low |

