## 7. iOS Compatibility

### Info.plist — Current Permissions
- ✅ `NSPhotoLibraryUsageDescription`
- ✅ `NSCameraUsageDescription`
- ✅ `NSPhotoLibraryAddUsageDescription`

### Missing Configuration

| Item | Status | Required By |
|------|--------|-------------|
| **`NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription`** | ❌ Missing | `geolocator`, `google_maps_flutter` — **app will crash on iOS when requesting location** |
| **`NSLocationAlwaysAndWhenInUseUsageDescription`** | ❌ Missing | `geolocator` (if always-on tracking needed) |
| **Podfile** | ❌ Not found | Required for CocoaPods — must run `flutter build ios` to generate, then configure minimum iOS version |
| **Minimum iOS version** | ⚠️ Unknown | Firebase, Google Maps, Sign in with Apple all require iOS 13+. Without a Podfile, this is unverified |
| **Google Maps iOS API key** | ❌ Missing | `google_maps_flutter` requires `GMSServices.provideAPIKey()` in `AppDelegate.swift` |
| **Sign in with Apple** | ⚠️ Needs config | Requires Apple Developer entitlements, capability enabled in Xcode, and `Runner.entitlements` file |
| **Google Sign-In** | ⚠️ Needs config | Requires `GoogleService-Info.plist` and URL scheme in Info.plist |
| **Firebase** | 🔴 Not initialized | `Firebase.initializeApp()` never called; `GoogleService-Info.plist` not present in iOS runner |
| **`flutter_secure_storage`** | ⚠️ Needs Keychain | May need Keychain Sharing capability enabled for iOS |
| **`path_provider`** | ⚠️ Implicit dep | Works on iOS but **not declared** in pubspec — fragile |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The app **will crash on iOS** when attempting to use location features because `NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription` is not in [Info.plist](file:///f:/Fodwa-App-main/ios/Runner/Info.plist).

