### Linting
- [analysis_options.yaml](file:///f:/Fodwa-App-main/analysis_options.yaml) has the linter include **commented out** (`# include: package:flutter_lints/flutter.yaml`)
- No lint rules are active — the project has **zero static analysis protection**
- `avoid_print` rule is commented out

### Potential Runtime Errors
1. `AppConfiguration.flavor` — `LateInitializationError` if any code path touches `isDev`/`isProd`
2. `AppKeys.section` has same storage key as `AppKeys.phone` (`"phone"`) — data collision
3. `DioClient.dio` is nullable and checked with `== null` but reinitialized inline — race condition possible
4. Arabic content in `StaticList.sections` in [app_constants.dart](file:///f:/Fodwa-App-main/lib/core/utils/app_constants.dart) — appears to be leftover from another project

