---

> **Bottom line:** The project has a reasonable architectural foundation (Clean Architecture in Auth/Profile, BLoC pattern, DI with get_it) but suffers from **critical security issues** (exposed secrets, disabled SSL), **dead dependencies** (GetX, 3 unused nav bars, Firebase without initialization), **no active linting**, and **iOS configuration gaps** that will prevent it from building or running correctly on Apple devices. Addressing the P0 items is essential before any deployment.
